ddf.minim
Interface Polyphonic

All Known Implementing Classes:
AudioOutput
public interface Polyphonic

Polyphonic describes an object that can have multiple AudioSignals attached to it. It is implemented by AudioOutput.

Author:
Damien Di Fede
